            <fr:title text="cone over a simplicial set">cone over a simplicial set</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  Given a simplicial set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>, the <html:strong>cone</html:strong> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X^\triangleleft ]]></fr:tex> is defined by the <fr:link href="/forest/htt-000B/" title="join of (augmented) simplicial set" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/htt-000B/" display-uri="htt-000B" type="local">join</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1 \star  X]]></fr:tex> with the singleton. Dually, the <html:strong>cocone</html:strong> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X^\triangleright ]]></fr:tex> is defined by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X \star  1]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
